# To--do-web-App
# 📝 To-Do Web Application

## 📌 Task Description
Develop a basic to-do web app that allows users to:
- Add tasks
- Organize tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Edit tasks
- Set date and time

---

## 🚀 Features
✔ Add new tasks  
✔ Edit tasks  
✔ Delete tasks  
✔ Mark tasks as completed  
✔ Add date & time to tasks  

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

---

## 📂 Project Structure

---

## ⚡ How It Works

### ➕ Add Task
Enter task + date/time and click Add

### ✅ Complete Task
Click on task text to mark complete

### ✏ Edit Task
Click Edit button to modify task

### ❌ Delete Task
Click Delete to remove task

---

## ▶️ How to Run
1. Download or clone repository
2. Open `index.html` in browser

